      <byline class="print_byline">By Renwick McLean (NYT)</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Mclean, Renwick</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Madrid, Spain, Mayor Alberto Ruiz-Gallardon announces that 28-story office building consumed by recent fire will have to be demolished (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Madrid's mayor, Alberto Ruiz-Gallardón, said the smoldering 28-story office building that caught fire over the weekend was too heavily damaged to be repaired and would have to be demolished.</p>
        <p>Renwick McLean (NYT)</p>
